OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHow a gay TV drama changed 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpeople's lives             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Queer as Folk has been heralded as     
OL,6, life-changing - and even life-saving.  
OL,8,FFirst broadcast 25 years ago, the TV   
OL,9,Fseries depicted three characters living
OL,10,Fin Manchester's Gay Village in a frank,
OL,11,Ffunny and explicit way that had not    
OL,12,Fbeen seen on UK TV before.             
OL,14,FPopular soaps like EastEnders had      
OL,15,Ffeatured gay relationships, but such   
OL,16,Fportrayals were rare and controversial.
OL,18,FWelsh screenwriter Russell T Davies'   
OL,19,Fseries came to be regarded as a        
OL,20,Fmilestone in LGBTQ+ representation.    
